<p><strong>Key takeaways from this chapter</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Gold and Silver are correlated both on an intraday basis and on an end of day basis.</li>
<li>Gold and Silver make a good pair for trading based on the ‘Pair trading technique’.</li>
<li>Silver does not have a great correlation with crude oil.</li>
<li>There are 4 variants of silver traded on MCX.</li>
<li>The main Silver contract has a lot size of 30 kgs and requires a margin close to Rs.75,000/-.</li>
<li>The average margin requirement for silver is roughly between 5-6% of the contract value.</li>
<li>Technical analysis works quite well on Silver.</li>
</ol>
